         <abstract id="aspace_f7b822aa609327930e5f82bb5124b6cd">Lectures and research notes on Indian civilization, religion and philology. Included also are lecture notes taken while he was studying in Berlin (1867-1868). Several of the lectures were prepared for presentation at meetings of the American Oriental Society.</abstract>
